				+ "\nFisher does not consider why a pencil can talk and go back to the desk in order to draw an axe.");
						Fisher.getsusage();
						answer = sc.next();
					}
					if(answer.equalsIgnoreCase("egg")){
						System.out.println("Pa! There is a sound comes behind"
